# âœ… **ESSENTIAL FEATURES (Keep These)**

These are the **minimum required features** for your polling system to work correctly and securely.

## **1. User (Voter) Registration & Login**

* Voter signs up
* Admin approves voter
* System assigns a voterId after approval
  â†’ Needed so only verified voters can cast votes.

---

## **2. Candidate Registration + Approval**

* Voter can request to become a candidate
* Admin approves candidates
  â†’ Needed for generating the ballot options.

---

## **3. Create an Election (Admin)**

* Admin creates an election title
  â†’ Needed because elections contain candidates & votes.

*(Time window is optional â€” see below)*

---

## **4. Voting Process**

* Voter enters voterId to vote
* Ballot shows approved candidates
* Voter selects a candidate
* Vote is **hashed** and stored **without voterId**
* Voter marked as **hasVoted = true**
  â†’ Required for fair & anonymous voting.

---

## **5. Counting Votes**

* System counts hashed votes by candidateId
  â†’ Required to produce results.

---

## **6. Declare Results**

* Admin sees candidate vote counts
* Winner is displayed
  â†’ Required to conclude the election.

---

## **7. Wipe Votes After Results**

* Delete all vote rows for the election
* Keep only:

  * Winner
  * Candidate list
  * Final vote counts
    â†’ Required to maintain anonymity & database cleanliness.

